For 2026, its neighbors include 2025 and 2027 (directly before and after in sequence), and since it's almost at the start of a new layer (besides 2026, the other numbers would be part of completing the square ring with 47 as the side length), we'd include numbers around 2025 in the spiral sequence just completed and then surmise the surrounding values based on their position.

